name: A Balancing Act 8x10
description:
Carnival, Circus, Children's Art, Girls Room Art, Nursery Art Girl, Children's Decor, Girl Art Print,Nursery Art, Cute - Balancing Act 8x10

A little while ago, I watched Charlie Chaplin's The Circus (for maybe the tenth time), and minutes before drifting off to Dreamland that same night, my mind was filled with imaginary stories of the inhabitants of such a wondrous place.

This is a depiction of Alma, connoisseur extraordinaire of equilibrium, and Sebastian, virtuoso of stilt walking, who, after having spent many years antagonizing each other, finally realized they had much more in common than either one of them would have ever thought, and decided to join acts and hearts alike.

This borderless print is reproduced from a painting by me. It measures 8x10 inch., and will feel right at home in any standard 8x10 inch frame or matte.

It is printed on lovely, velvety, archival acid-free matte paper, with archival pigment inks, both of which are tested and guaranteed against smudge, scratch, and water, and are fade resistant for up to 108 years.

All prints are signed and dated on the back, and will come to you safely sealed in a cello sleeve and a protective stiff envelope.

name: A Tea Party 8x10 Print
description:
Alice In Wonderland Art, Girl Art Print, Nursery Art, Children's Art, Girls Room Art, Decor, Cute, Art for Children - A Tea Party 8x10 Print

It's not very hard to entertain a group of white rabbits...All one needs is plenty of tea, an assortment of muffins, delicious scones and pies, and, of course, plenty of carrot cake!

I have long wanted to pay a small tribute to one of my favorite books, the ever-enchanting-no-matter-how-many-times-you-have-read-it-before, Alice in Wonderland.

'A Tea Party' is a print reproduction of one of the paintings from my "Curiouser and Curiouser" series, whose theme revolves around an imaginary depiction of Lewis Carroll's Alice In Wonderland. The collection depicts a world filled with curious characters in beautiful vintage-inspired colours, set in a dreamy, fairytale atmosphere.
